description: Thousands of chickens are being culled as H5N8 bird flu spreads in Europe.
title: Bird flu: Culls in Dutch and German farms over outbreaks
title_page: Bird flu: Culls in Dutch and German farms over outbreaks - BBC News
maintext: Containment zones have been set up around the farms, as well as around the north German farm in Oland, Nordfriesland. Farmers have been urged to keep their poultry indoors.
